    <div class="faq_title" style="margin-top: 5px">
      General
    </div>
    <div class="faq_question">
      What is <b>sendd.me</b>?
    </div>
    <div class="faq_answer">
      sendd.me is a platform for social deliveries.<br>
      Whenever you go somewhere, and feel like making some money on the way, deliver for someone and get paid!<br>
      Alternatively, find a Transporter to deliver what you want, where and when you want it!
    </div>
    <div class="faq_question">
      How does it work?
    </div>
    <div class="faq_answer">
      We're trying very hard to make it very easy for you.<br><br>
      Feel like making money transporting something?
      <ul>
        <li>Go to <b>Browse Senders</b> at the top.</li>
        <li>Pick an available  Delivery Request.</li>
        <li>Get confirmed by the Sender.</li>
        <li>Perform delivery.</li>
        <li>Get paid!</li>
      </ul>
      Need to deliver somewhere quickly?
      <ul>
        <li>Go to <b>Find Transporters</b> at the top.</li>
        <li>Pick an available  Delivery Suggestion.</li>
        <li>Get confirmed by the Transporter.</li>
        <li>Get your things delivered!</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="faq_question">
      I haven't found a Delivery Request/Suggestion which was right for me
    </div>
    <div class="faq_answer">
      Hey, that can happen to anyone!<br>
      We also provide the ability to add your own Delivery Requests/Suggestions!<br><br>
      Want to add your own Delivery Suggestion?
      <ul>
        <li>Go to <b>Browse Senders</b> at the top.</li>
        <li>Click <b>Add your own suggestion</b>.</li>
        <li>Take 15 seconds to add necessary details.</li>
        <li>Get accepted by many Senders.</li>
        <li>Confirm your Sender.</li>
        <li>Perform delivery.</li>
        <li>Get paid!</li>
      </ul>
      Want to add your own Delivery Request?
      <ul>
        <li>Go to <b>Find Transporters</b> at the top.</li>
        <li>Click <b>Add your own request</b>.</li>
        <li>Take 15 seconds to add necessary details.</li>
        <li>Get accepted by many Transporters.</li>
        <li>Confirm your Transporter.</li>
        <li>Get your things delivered!</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="faq_question">
      Can I edit the details in my Delivery Request/Suggestion?
    </div>
    <div class="faq_answer">
      Yes you can, as long as your Delivery Request/Suggestion hasn't been accepted by anyone yet.<br>
      Simply go to your Delivery Request/Suggestions's page, and click <b>Edit</b>.
    </div>
    <div class="faq_question">
      Can I post a number of Delivery Requests/Suggestions?
    </div>
    <div class="faq_answer">
      Absolutely! We encourage our Senders and Transporters to post as many deliveries as they like.<br>
      Become a top rated Sender or Transporter quicker, earn more money and deliver your stuff quickly!
    </div>
    <div class="faq_question">
      OK, sounds cool. what's in it for sendd.me?
    </div>
    <div class="faq_answer">
      Besides making the world a better, more efficient and environment friendly place, we also charge 15% out of each delivery cost.
    </div>
    <div class="faq_question">
      I don't know anyone on <b>sendd.me</b>. How can I trust them?
    </div>
    <div class="faq_answer">
      We do our best to verify all of our Transporters and Senders.<br>
      We do so in 4 ways:
      <ul>
        <li>We verify your mobile phone number (Cannot accept/confirm deliveries without this).</li>
        <li>We verify your Facebook account.</li>
        <li>We verify your Email address.</li>
        <li>We have a simple, yet effective user rating system.</li>
      </ul>
      If you are good, and have verified all of your details, others will give you good reviews, and you will get confirmed for more deliveries.
      Make a reputation for yourself, and become a top Transporter or Sender!
    </div>
    <div class="faq_question">
      What are you going to do with my details?
    </div>
    <div class="faq_answer">
      We are committed to never exposing any of your details.<br>
      The only exceptions are the following cases:
      <ul>
        <li>A Sender confirms a Transporter for his Delivery Request, after which both their mobile phone numbers become visible only to the both of them.</li>
        <li>A Sender authorizes Preapproved Payment for a Delivery Suggestion, after which both their mobile phone numbers become visible only to the both of them.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="faq_question">
      How can I contact another user?
    </div>
    <div class="faq_answer">
      We provide 3 ways of communicating with other users:
      <ul>
        <li>Leave a comment to creator of Delivery Request/Suggestion (Visible for everyone)</li>
        <li>After accepting a Delivery Request/Suggestion, you can send a direct message to its creator (Visible for the 2 of you alone).</li>
        <li>After being confirmed for a Delivery Request/Suggestion, you can call its creator via mobile phone (Visible for the 2 of you alone)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="faq_question">
      How does the payment system work?
    </div>
    <div class="faq_anwser">
      We process all payments through PayPal.<br>
      For each delivery, the Sender must authorize a Preapproved Payment:
      <ul>
        <li>For your own Delivery Requests - a Preapproved Payment for the amount you set when creating the Delivery Request.</li>
        <li>For a Transporter's Delivery Suggestion - a Preapproved Payment for the amount set by the Transporter when creating the Delivery Suggestion.</li>
      </ul>
      When the delivery is complete, PayPal will transfer the Preapproved Payment amount to the Transporter.
    </div>
    <div class="faq_question">
      Should I add all the details to my Delivery Request/Suggestion?
    </div>
    <div class="faq_answer">
      You don't have to, but you definitely should!<br>
      Why, you ask?<br>
      When you add all the details to your Delivery Request/Suggestion, it is then marked as <b>has all details</b>.<br>
      This gives you 2 things:
      <ul>
        <li>Priority in our lists</li>
        <li>More Transporters/Senders coming your way!</li>
      </ul>
      That's why it's very important to fill out all the details.
    </div>
