    <div class="faq_question">
      When do I get paid for the task?
    </div>
    <div class="faq_answer">
      You get paid after you have successfully performed a delivery, which can be either:
      <ul>
        <li>A Sender's Delivery Request of which you are the confirmed Transporter.</li>
        <li>Your own Delivery Suggestion accepted and confirmed by a Sender.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="faq_question">
      Do I need to pay taxes?
    </div>
    <div class="faq_answer">
      You need to pay taxes according to the law in your state/country. Nevertheless, in most countries there is a minimum for income tax exemption.
    </div>
